          <title>Utah Passes Landmark Legislation Requiring App Stores to Verify Users' Ages - The Latest in Children's Online Safety</title>
          <description><![CDATA[Utah becomes the first state to pass legislation requiring app stores to verify users' ages and get parental consent for minors to download apps, sparking a debate over who should be responsible for verifying ages.]]></description>
